<p>He is buried now about 1500 yards from Bapaume and over his head is a cross made by men of this Bn, in token of their love and respect to a man who was a man and a hero to the last.</p>
<p>I remain<br/>Yours very Sincerely,<br/>Geoff H. Leslie<br/>Lieut</p>
